  <brief_title>Stimulation of the Diaphragm in Patients With Severe Heart Failure Following Heart Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Biventricular Pacing and Stimulation of the Diaphragm in Patients With Severe Heart Failure Following Heart Surgery (Epiphrenic II Pilot Trial)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
